    {
      "id": "pathshala_upanishads_chapter_1_1.1",
      "ref": "1.1",
      "chapter": 1,
      "sanskrit": "ईशा वास्यमिदं सर्वं यत्किञ्च जगत्यां जगत् । तेन त्यक्तेन भुञ्जीथा मा गृधः कस्यस्विद्धनम् ॥",
      "transliteration": "īśā vāsyamidaṁ sarvaṁ yatkiñca jagatyāṁ jagat | tena tyaktena bhuñjīthā mā gṛdhaḥ kasyasviddhanam ||",
      "text": "All this, whatever moves in this moving world, is enveloped by the Lord. Therefore, find your enjoyment in renunciation; do not covet what belongs to others.",
